lead_paragraph: Two people with knowledge of the situation tell The Associated Press that the Oklahoma City Thunder have agreed to terms with Steven Adams and Victor Oladipo on four-year contract extensions.

headline.print_headline: AP Sources: Thunder Lock Up Oladipo, Adams
